caption.title: Weekly percentage of influenza strains among all lab-confirmed positive tests reported to Taiwan CDC by the contracted laboratories.
caption.p: (a) week 1, 2008-week 18, 2011; (b) week 20, 2011-week 18; 2014, with virus strains B in blue, AH1 in broken green, A(H1N1)pdm09 in green, AH3 in red, and H3N2 in broken red.
